V.





Tomorrow is our wedding anniversary—21 years, if you can believe it.4





TO: ELIZABETH MARINEL ALLAN AND MARUSSYA MARINEL

ALS, 1 p. M. Juliar.





8 Craigie Circle

Cambridge 38, Mass.

22 May, 1946

Dear Marussya and Lisa,

This paper is quite undescribably lovely. Thank you!

